data.description:
This beautiful and affordable well constructed log home with nice open floor plan is just minutes from Deep Lake! Enjoy your very own jetted tub in  the main bathroom. Reverse Osmosis water filtration system, central heating and air conditioning. Includes barn, wood shed and one bedroom in-law set up. A rare find! New Density regulations allow one house per lot, this one has 2 (grandfather clause) New paved highways. Hunting and fishing nearby. Wildlife abounds in this area and includes deer, elk, bear, turkeys and an occasional mountain lion sighting. Wildlife watchers dream come true. Miles and miles of 4 wheeler trails. This is a great place to raise your kids and/or animals. This listing includes adjacent lot of just over one acre.

***Additions of improvements will increase price***
data.whatILove: Quiet, abundance of birds and wildlife, beautiful area in all seasons, on school bus route. Property partially backed by rock formations that helps keep the wind down.
